                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17640912-21-off115 t17640912-21-crimeloc118"></join>. On the 30th of July, I went out of my shop; backwards, into the kitchen; I generally shut the shop door, and lock it, but do not take the key out. About eight at night, I seeing the door open, went in, and missed a silver watch: I went about with written papers to the pawnbrokers the next morning, and when I got home, 
               <persName id="t17640912-21-person207">
                  Mr. 
                  Griffice 
               <interp inst="t17640912-21-person207" type="surname" value="Griffice"></interp>
